(香港)|羅蘭]]合作為[[香港海洋公園|海洋公園]]「十月全城哈囉喂」代言<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x_6zCjDHpIs&list=UUHH0RdJv0dPTHn23S7AbtdA |title=【羅蘭姐x夏蕙姨x鵬哥】哈囉喂全日祭廣告至爆登場！ |last= |first= |date=2014 |website= |publisher=香港海洋公園 |access-date=2020-07-12 |quote= |archive-date=2015-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716003135/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x_6zCjDHpIs&list=UUHH0RdJv0dPTHn23S7AbtdA |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年4月化身美人魚拍攝保護海洋宣傳影片，反對政府推行[[明日大嶼願景|明日大嶼願景]]填海工程，呼籲守護香港海洋<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.greenpeace.org/hongkong/issues/health/update/1636/美人魚黃夏蕙，無畏愛海洋 |title=美人魚黃夏蕙，無畏愛海洋 |last= |first= |date=2019-04-03 |website= |publisher=綠色和平 |access-date=2020-07-12 |quote= |archive-date=2020-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713231419/https://www.greenpeace.org/hongkong/issues/health/update/1636/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BA%BA%E9%AD%9A%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%A1%E7%95%8F%E6%84%9B%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===其他資料===
黃夏蕙有見昔日好友[[司徒關佩英|司徒關佩英]]、[[鄧碧雲|鄧碧雲]]、[[鳳凰女|鳳凰女]]和[[新馬師曾|新馬師曾]]伉儷相繼離世{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}，於是每年在農曆新年前到[[黃大仙祠_(香港)|黃大仙廟]]與人爭上「頭炷香」<ref>{{cite news | title=有段故！黃夏蕙親解年年上頭炷香原因 | url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170429/bkn-20170429044515989-0429_00862_001.html | page= | publisher=東網 | date=2017-04-29 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712021741/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170429/bkn-20170429044515989-0429_00862_001.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，以延續與五人曾經一起上香的活動回憶{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。有關情況間中會被香港電視台拍攝到<ref>{{cite news | title=【新年2019】萬眾期待黃夏蕙上頭炷香！回顧5個經典生肖造型 | url=https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/206695/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B42019-%E8%90%AC%E7%9C%BE%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%85%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%E4%B8%8A%E9%A0%AD%E7%82%B7%E9%A6%99-%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A75%E5%80%8B%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%82%96%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B/1 | page= | publisher=港生活 | date=2019-02-04 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712070705/https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/206695/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B42019-%E8%90%AC%E7%9C%BE%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%85%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%E4%B8%8A%E9%A0%AD%E7%82%B7%E9%A6%99-%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A75%E5%80%8B%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%82%96%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B/1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，她於2006年初，與其夫潘炳烈一同捲入一宗金沙[[詐騙|騙案]]中<ref>{{cite news | title=代潘炳烈出面否認為中間人黃夏蕙也險墮金沙騙局 | url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060123/5597062 | page= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2006-01-23 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714114535/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060123/5597062 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後證實與案件無關。同年，其家中的[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[女傭|女傭]]，偷取黃夏蕙超過20萬元的名貴[[珠寶|珠寶]]<ref>{{cite news | title=菲傭偷廿萬珠寶走路 黃夏蕙報警求助 | url=http://the-sun.orisun.com/channels/ent/20060215/20060215001614_0000.html | page= | publisher=太陽報 | date=2006-02-15 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2014-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226230818/http://the-sun.orisun.com/channels/ent/20060215/20060215001614_0000.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==個人生活==
黃夏蕙初入影圈時期曾和當時[[香港電影#粵語電影|粵語片]]演員[[林蛟|林蛟]]拍拖。拍畢《火》便透過[[紅綫女|紅綫女]]介紹結識已婚名門[[律師|律師]][[胡百全|胡百全]]{{noteTag|name=守下留情1}}。未幾被對方追求展開情侶關係{{noteTag|name=守下留情1}}，並因而放棄幕前電影事業{{noteTag|name=守下留情1}}，定居[[跑馬地|跑馬地]][[山村道|山村道]]和[[麥當勞道|麥當勞道]]超過四年{{noteTag|name=守下留情1}}。且為他誕下四子二女；私生子女全部冠胡姓，胡百全留了一份基金支付他們的生活費用<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/interview/%e5%a8%9b%e6%a8%82123/20160109-7600 |title=擺70圍酒 派2500張帖黃夏蕙搞亂潘炳烈壽宴 |last= |first= |date=2016-01-09 |website= |publisher=明周 |access-date=2020-07-12 |quote= |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712151122/https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/interview/%e5%a8%9b%e6%a8%82123/20160109-7600 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其中長女[[胡蓮娜|胡蓮娜]]現是[[九龍巴士|九龍巴士]]和[[載通國際|載通國際]]的[[公司秘書|公司秘書]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2003/0404/62/cwp116_c.pdf |title=董事簡介及高級行政人員 |last= |first= |date=2003 |website= |publisher=九龍巴士 |access-date=2020-07-12 |quote= |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712050650/https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2003/0404/62/cwp116_c.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>黃夏蕙後來在1983年與[[賽車手|賽車手]][[潘炳烈|潘炳烈]]結婚。另外，由於多年的舞台生活，使她只懂得舞台[[化粧|化粧]]而不懂得日常生活的裝扮，以致外貌看起來誇張異相，因此令人懷疑她是為了掩飾[[整形|整容]]痕跡。亦令其成為[[香港傳媒|香港傳媒]]及網上社群[[惡搞文化|惡搞]]的其中一個對象，例如香港一本光碟月刊《POP》（已停刊）曾用「黃下胃」作為月刊內虛擬建築物的設計師的名字。

除此之外，黃夏蕙被指喜歡標奇立異，以博取見報機會。其言行多番成為他人談論的話題。因為經常出席名人[[葬禮|喪禮]]而有「殯儀之星」的稱號<ref>{{cite news | title=黃夏蕙走遍喪禮 | url=https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20061013/6400535 | page= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2006-10-13 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714133420/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20061013/6400535 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。又黃夏蕙是[[新馬師曾|新馬師曾]]和[[洪金梅|洪金梅]]（祥嫂）的好友<ref>{{cite news | title=與祥哥夫婦極老友 黃夏蕙開聲就成事 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqoorcFBQ8m%2FmH&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=84&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=13 | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1991-08-21 | accessdate=2020-07-13 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713052634/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqoorcFBQ8m%2FmH&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=84&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=祥嫂洪金梅逝世 享年73歲 | url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/07/03/EN1907030003.htm | page= | publisher=文匯報 | date=2019-07-03 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715041116/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/07/03/EN1907030003.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[鄧家爭產事件|鄧家爭產事件]]中力撐祥嫂，因此帶來「娛樂圈攝石人」的稱號<ref>{{cite news | title=娛圈攝石人新聞多多 | url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20040827/4268256 | page= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2004-08-27 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713150442/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20040827/4268256 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年7月，黃更花費百萬，為自己舉行[[生前喪禮|生前喪禮]]<ref>{{cite news | title=港星黃夏蕙斥百萬辦生前葬禮 死後捐器官 | url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714144559/http://ent.sina.com.hk/news/-2-1125583/1.html | page= | publisher=新浪娛樂 | date=2014-07-14| accessdate=2020-07-12|quote= }}</ref>。翌年4月，黃夏蕙以素顏嚇走入屋爆竊賊人一事獲日本[[富士電視台|富士電視台]]節目《{{Link-ja|世界HOTジャーナル|世界HOTジャーナル}}》採訪<ref>{{cite news | title=【素顏的威力】寓所凌晨遭「爆格」夏蕙姨憑素顏 嚇走賊人 | url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20150404/53602349 | page= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2015-04-04 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115425/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20150404/53602349 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=素顏力量強大？資深女港星夜裡「一個眼神」嚇跑竊賊 | url=http://www.setn.com/E/News.aspx?NewsID=69046 | page= | publisher=三立新聞 | date=2015-04-06 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2016-03-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319031759/http://www.setn.com/e/news.aspx?newsid=69046 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bHvrCI2Nocc |title=世界HOTジャーナル　強い女性SP |last= |first= |date=2015-04-24 |website= |publisher=富士電視台 |access-date=2020-07-12 |quote= |archive-date=2020-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505221856/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bHvrCI2Nocc&gl=US&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

而黃關注社會時事的同時，會參與一些[[社會運動|社會運動]]，例如在[[D&G禁止香港人攝影風波|D&G禁止香港人攝影風波]]中支持反名店霸權<ref>{{cite news | title=2000人圍攻8小時「影」衰D&G | url=https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120109/00176_003.html | page= | publisher=東方日報 | date=2012-01-09 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029051949/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120109/00176_003.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[葵青貨櫃碼頭工潮|葵青貨櫃碼頭工潮]]中支持碼頭工人等<ref>{{cite news | title=黃夏蕙BB扲$2,000 買生果撐工人 | url=https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20130414/ZRX7V4Q3XGZ76YUWTFANWGXCBM/ | page= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2013-04-14 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714221357/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20130414/ZRX7V4Q3XGZ76YUWTFANWGXCBM/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。也會在[[社交網路服務|社交網站]]樂於與網民互動，所以被網民稱她為「[[女神_(特定人群稱謂)|女神]]」和「夏蕙BB」<ref>{{cite news | title=夏蕙姨「除半罩」寸政府：最需要你的時候無出現過！ | url=https://news.now.com/home/entertainment/player?newsId=390083 | page= | publisher=now新聞 | date=2020-05-06 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712093057/https://news.now.com/home/entertainment/player?newsId=390083 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她曾經準備出戰2019年11月的[[2019年香港區議會選舉|區議會選舉]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/focus/local/20190821-166276 |title=88歲黃夏蕙擬參選區議員 「將開心帶俾市民」 |last= |first= |date=2020-01-16 |website= |publisher=明周 |access-date=2020-07-12 |quote= |archive-date=2019-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821161621/https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/focus/local/20190821-166276 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。目前成立了「夏蕙慈善基金」以實踐其慈善事業<ref>{{cite news | title=黃夏蕙專訪 | url=http://seattlechinesetimes.com/2019/06/14/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA/ | page= | publisher=西城時報 | date=2019-06-14 | accessdate=2020-07-12 | quote= | archive-date=2020-08-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825085209/http://seattlechinesetimes.com/2019/06/14/%e9%bb%83%e5%a4%8f%e8%95%99%e5%b0%88%e8%a8%aa/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

